{"_id":"bkqjtbn8hls","name":"Limited Degree","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Your Affliction is limited to no more than two degrees of effect. With two applications of this modifier, it is limited to no more than one degree of effect.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"euy8yf2uxq","name":"Activation","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>A power with this flaw requires an action to prepare or activate before any of its effects are usable. Move action is –1 point, standard action is –2 points.</p><p>Flat -1 or -2 points.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"m9or6fyn8rg","name":"Instant Recovery","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>The target of an Affliction effect with this modifier recovers automatically, no check required, at the end of the round in which the duration ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"79qi527ohbv","name":"Check Required","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An effect with this flaw requires a check of some sort—usually a skill check—with a base difficulty of 10, +1 for each additional rank in Check Required.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"ge4wl748ue","name":"Concentration","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Using a Concentration effect requires more concentration than normal. If you are unable to maintain your concentration, the effect ends.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"6ljnb5totjj","name":"Diminished Range","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the effect’s range increments by one step.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"k4rvl8l2sx","name":"Distracting","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Using a Distracting effect requires so much concentration or effort that you are vulnerable until the start of your next turn.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"33thzr991gv","name":"Grab-Based","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An attack with this flaw requires you to successfully grab and hold a target before the effect can be used.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"e22zcnneyw5","name":"Increased Action","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw increases the action required to use an effect by one step (Free to Move, Move to Standard, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"18ick4agc2j","name":"Limited","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An effect with this flaw only works under certain circumstances, or has a significant restriction on its use.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"yhbu7j16g8o","name":"Noticeable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>A continuous or permanent effect with this flaw is very noticeable (glows, makes a loud noise, etc.).</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"9fmp731jog","name":"Quirk","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>A Quirk is a minor flaw, often something specific to a character or power, that doesn’t quite rise to the level of a full -1 cost per rank flaw.</p><p>Flat -1 point.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"zz2tb65zy2m","name":"Reduced Range","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Each rank of this flaw reduces the range of an effect (Ranged to Close, etc.).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"ttyw4sq1qgf","name":"Resistible","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An effect with this flaw allows an additional resistance check, or is resisted by a different defense than usual.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"xpfegdzjehk","name":"Sense-Dependent","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>The target must be able to perceive the effect with a particular sense for it to work.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"7afheoqqu6v","name":"Side Effect","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>If you fail to use the effect properly, or even if you succeed, you suffer a negative side effect.</p><p>–1 or –2 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"0y7ssb0d9qif","name":"Tiring","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Using the effect is physically or mentally taxing, causing you to become fatigued.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"21sbpasxhac","name":"Uncontrolled","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>You have no control over when the effect activates or what it does; the GM decides.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"l1x800won6k","name":"Unreliable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An Unreliable effect only works some of the time (5 uses, or requires a check each time).</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"curcs26o4r5","name":"Feedback","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>You suffer damage when a manifestation of your effect is damaged.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"2eo0ux4z898","name":"Inaccurate","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An effect with this flaw is hard to control or wildly inaccurate. Each rank gives you a –2 penalty to attack checks.</p><p>Flat -1 point per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"4cnd1ld1tlx","name":"Permanent","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>A continuous effect with this flaw becomes permanent in duration. It cannot be turned off and cannot be improved using extra effort.</p><p>–1 cost per rank.</p>","cout":{"fixe":false,"rang":true,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"rtzhzm7nxqn","name":"Removable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>Removable applies to the power as a whole. The flaw is worth –1 point per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -1 point per 5 points.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":1}}}
{"_id":"yjlsulr7agp","name":"Easily Removable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An easily removable power can be taken away with a disarm or grab action. The flaw is worth –2 points per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -2 points per 5 points.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":2}}}